---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Header from '../components/astro/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/astro/Footer.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About | Tech Blog" description="About this blog">
  <Header />
  <main class="flex-1">
    <div class="container max-w-4xl py-10">
      <div class="prose prose-slate dark:prose-invert">
        <h1>About</h1>
        <p>
          Welcome to my tech blog! This is a place where I share my thoughts on web development,
          programming, and technology.
        </p>
        <h2>About This Blog</h2>
        <p>This blog is built with modern web technologies:</p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Astro</strong> - Static site generator with excellent performance</li>
          <li><strong>Svelte</strong> - Interactive components with minimal JavaScript</li>
          <li><strong>shadcn-svelte</strong> - Beautiful UI components</li>
          <li><strong>Tailwind CSS</strong> - Utility-first CSS framework</li>
          <li><strong>TypeScript</strong> - Type-safe code with esbuild compilation</li>
        </ul>
        <p>
          The site features dark mode, code syntax highlighting, and is fully responsive. All
          content is written in MDX, allowing for rich, interactive blog posts.
        </p>
        <h2>Contact</h2>
        <p>Feel free to reach out or follow along:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>
            GitHub: <a href="https://github.com/yish0" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"
              >@yish0</a
            >
          </li>
          <li>RSS Feed: <a href="/rss.xml">Subscribe</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</BaseLayout>
